title: Tuesday Post Show (3-23-21)

description:
We try out yet another Post Show introduction. Bobby wants something more Retro. Bobby on doing Zoom with listeners with hard hitting questions. Guy who bungee jumped with butt piercings. Kylie Jenner gets backlash for promoting friend’s GoFundMe. Plus a guy who tried to escape the police officers on horseback. Bobby thinks he could escape 3 police cars.
